Marka hore, xididdada ayaa isbedela marka la eego nuqulkooda RNA.
Marka la barbardhigo fayrasyada kale ee hal-jibaarka ah ee RNA, heerka isbeddelka la qiyaasay ee CoVs waxaa loo tixgelin karaa inuu yahay "dhexdhexaad" ilaa "sare" oo leh celcelis ahaan 10 ilaa 4 isbeddello sanadkiiba hal goob, 2 iyadoo ku xiran marxaladda isbeddelka CoV ee isbeddelka cusub.
