Waxaa xiiso leh in Remdesivir nucleotide-ka loo yaqaano inuu ka hortago is-qaybinta CoVs adoo xakameynaya enzymes-ka exoribonuclease iyo RNA-dependent RNA polymerase.
Remdesivir waa mid ka mid ah wakiilada ugu guulaha badan ee ka hortagga fayraska SARS-CoV-2 ee lagu tijaabiyay daaweynta tijaabada ah.
