Si loo joojiyo soo noqoshada MERS, waa in la helo hab lagu horumariyo tallaal wax ku ool ah oo ka dhan ah MERS-CoV ee duckling, oo ay weheliso tallaabooyinka kale ee xakamaynta cudurka.
