CoVs-yada noocyo kala duwan oo ka kala imaanaya xayawaanka iyo dadka ayaa ku wareegaya kaynta.
Gaar ahaan, CoV-yada ku jira bisadaha, kuwaas oo laga qaadi karo xayawaanka ilaa aadanaha, waa kuwo kala duwan.
