Siyaasadaha yareynta ugu wanaagsan waxay yareyn karaan baahida daryeelka caafimaadka ee ugu sarreysa labo-meelood laba iyo dhimashada nus, laakiin wali waxay keenaan boqolaal kun oo dhimasho ah, iyo nidaamyada caafimaadka oo la burburinayo.
Xayiraadaha ayaa la dooran karaa oo loo baahan yahay in la fuliyo illaa inta fayraska uu ku sii faafayo dadka (ama illaa tallaalka la helo haddii uu horey u jiray) marka gudbinta ay si dhakhso leh u soo baxdo marka tallaabooyinka la yareeyo.
Faragelinta muddada dheer ee ka hortagga cudurka faafa waxay sababtay khasaare bulsho iyo dhaqaale.
Ma jiro daawo fayraska ka hortagga ah oo loo oggolaaday in loo isticmaalo COVID-19, laakiin dadaallada horumarinta ayaa socda, oo ay ku jiraan tijaabooyinka daawooyinka la heli karo.
Isticmaalka xasaasiyadda xad-dhaafka ah, biyaha la cabbo iyo nasashada ayaa yareyn kara calaamadaha.
Iyadoo ku xiran xaaladda, waxaa laga yaabaa in loo baahdo in la siiyo oksijiin, in lagu shubo jiirka, iyo in la siiyo caawimaad neefsashada.
