Bishii Maarso 24, 2020, Ra'iisul Wasaaraha Shiinaha Li Keqiang ayaa sheegay in faafitaanka kiisaska gudaha si weyn loo xakameeyay, iyo in cudurka uu ku faafay Shiinaha.
