Tallaalka tijaabada ah ee laga helay mid ka mid ah istaraatiijiyadahan ayaa la tijaabin doonaa badbaadada iyo waxtarka. Bishii Maarso 16, 2020, tijaabooyinkii ugu horreeyay ee tallaalka ayaa ka bilaabmay afar mutadawiciin ah oo ku sugan Seattle.
Tallaalka waxaa ku jira hiddo-wadaha aan khatarta ka lahayn fayraska sababa cudurka.Ku xoojinta ku tiirsanaanta antibody-ka ayaa lagu soo jeediyay inay caqabad ku tahay horumarinta tallaalka SARS-COV-2, laakiin waa mid dood leh.
Waxaa jiray in ka badan 300 tijaabooyin daaweyn oo firfircoon oo socda ilaa Abriil 2020.
Toddoba tijaabo ayaa lagu qiimeeyay daaweynta la oggolaaday ee cudurka qandhada, oo ay ku jiraan afar daraasadood oo ku saabsan hydrogen, hydrogen, ama chlorine.
Daawooyinka fayraska ee dib loo isticmaalo ayaa inta badan ka caawiyay cilmi baarista Shiinaha, iyadoo ay jiraan sagaal tijaabooyin marxaladda III ah oo lagu sameeyay Remdesivir oo ka dhacay dalal badan, sida lagu sheegay warbixinta dhammaadka Abriil.
Dib u eegista joogtada ah ee horumarka caafimaad ee tallaalka COVID-19 iyo daawooyinka la doonayo ayaa la soo bandhigay, laga bilaabo Abriil 2020. Daawooyin badan oo ka hortagga fayraska ayaa la qiimeynayaa si loogu daaweeyo COVID-19 Remdesivir, Chloroquine iyo Hydroxychloroquine, Lopinavir/Ritonavir iyo Lopinavir/Ritonavir oo lagu daray Interferon beta.
Waxaa jiray caddeyn ku meel gaadh ah oo ku saabsan waxtarka Remdesivir bishii Maarso 2020.
Isbeddelka xaaladda ayaa la arkay marka la daaweeyo remdesivir.
Tijaabooyinka tijaabada ah ee wajiga III ayaa ka socda Mareykanka, Shiinaha iyo Talyaaniga. Chloroquine, oo horey loogu isticmaali jiray daaweynta kansarka, ayaa lagu bartay Shiinaha bishii Febraayo 2020 iyadoo natiijooyin horudhac ah.
Laakiin waxaa jira baaqyo lagu doonayo in dib loo eego cilmi baarista.
Hay'adaha caafimaadka ee Kuuriya iyo Shiinaha ayaa ku talinaya isticmaalka chlorokine.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, Machadka Virology ee Wuhan wuxuu kugula talinayaa in la isticmaalo hal garaam oo keliya, iyo laba garaam oo keliya waxay halis ugu jiraan khatarta iyo dhimashada.
Bishii Maarso 28, 2020, FDA waxay soo saartay ogeysiis furan oo u oggolaanaysa isticmaalka degdegga ah ee hydroxychloroquine iyo chloroquine iyadoo la raacayo go'aanka dhakhaatiirta ee daaweynta bukaannada qaba COVID-19. Tilmaamaha 7-aad ee Shiinaha ayaa sidoo kale oggolaaday isticmaalka interferon, ribavirin ama umifenovir ee ka dhanka ah COVID-19.
Xogta hore waxay muujineysaa in heerarka sare ee ribavirin loo baahan yahay in lagu xakameeyo SARS-CoV-2 ee tijaabooyinka caafimaad.
Nitazoxanide waxaa la soo jeediyay daraasado dheeri ah ka dib markii la ogaaday in ay xakameyso SARS-CoV-2 heerar hoose. Daraasado kale ayaa muujinaya in ay jirto sii deynta borotiinka iyada oo loo marayo qanjirka 'serine protease 2' (TMPRSS2), oo lagama maarmaan u ah SARS-CoV-2 inuu galaan unugyada iyada oo loo marayo ACE2 receptor.
Daraasadaha ku saabsan isticmaalka chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine ama la'aanta azithromycin waa mid aad u adag, maadaama ay jiraan difaacyo ka yimid ururada caafimaadka oo sheegaya in daaweynta loo isticmaalo iyada oo aan la sameyn daraasadaha. Oseltamivir ma joojinayo SARS-CoV-2 mana kaalinayo daaweynta COVID-19.
Kororka cytokine-ka ayaa laga yaabaa inuu yahay natiijada marxaladda dambe ee COVID-19.
Caddayn ayaa la helay oo muujinaysa in hydroxychloroquine ay xakameyso koritaanka unugyada cytokine. Tocilizumab ayaa sidoo kale la soo bandhigay daaweynta, sida laga soo xigtay Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka Shiinaha, kadib markii daraasad yar la dhammeystiray.
Waxaa lagu wadaa tijaabooyin aan kala sooc lahayn oo wajiga 2aad ah oo heer qaran ah Talyaaniga kadib markii ay soo bandhigtay natiijooyin wanaagsan oo ku saabsan dadka qaba cudurka daran.
Marka lagu daro baaritaanka serum-ka ee loo yaqaan 'fluoride blood test' si loo ogaado Cytokine Storms, waxaa loola jeedaa in laga hortago isbeddellada noocan oo kale ah ee loo tixgeliyo inay yihiin sababaha dhimashada dadka qaba saameynta qaarkood.
Daawada loo yaqaan 'interleukin-6' ayaa waxaa ansixiyay FDA iyadoo lagu saleynayo daraasad kiis dambe ah oo loogu talagalay daaweynta cudurka 'steroid refractory cytokine' ee ka dhasha walaaca 'steroid' ee ka dhasha CAR T-cell therapy sanadkii 2017.
Ilaa hadda ma jiro caddayn la xakameyn karo oo muujinaysa in tocilizumab uu yahay daaweyn wax ku ool ah oo loogu talagalay CRS.
Wareejinta antibodies-ka la qasi jiray oo ay soo saartey nidaamka difaaca ee dadka ka soo kabsaday COVID-19 oo loo gudbiyo dadka u baahan ayaa loo tixgelinayaa inay tahay habka tallaalka ee aan loo isticmaalin tallaalka.
Istaraatiijiyaddan ayaa loo tijaabiyay SARS iyadoo natiijooyin aan la hubin.
Xanuunka ayaa ah habka ficilka ee daaweynta antibody-ka aan firfircooneyn ay u hagaajin karto difaaca ka dhanka ah SARS-CoV-2.
